title: Binfer  3.3.3.0
description:
Binfer  3.3.3.0


Freeware.  It is completely free to install and use.




Binfer is a file transfer application for sending & receiving large files without uploading them on any servers. Binfer allows you to send large files such as HD video, high resolution images, and complex documents to anyone over the Internet.

Key features include:

Direct computer to computer transfers.
Send from Binfer and receive on mobile devices.
Web Pickup allows you to receive files from your website directly to Binfer.
Web Drop allows you to drag and drop folders.
Send and receive from behind firewalls and NAT devices.
View live transfer status.
AES 128 bit encryption.
With Binfer you can receive large files directly to your computer from anyone, via a web browser, thereby eliminating large email attachment issues. By using Binfer you can cut the cost and complexity of using FTP clients and servers. Also Binfer allows you to transfer at super-fast speeds whilst preserving the privacy and confidentiality of your data.

All in all, Binfer is a really useful tool that has a standard explorer style interface and is really easy to use. So, if you are in the habit of dealing with large files on a regular basis, try Binfer as an alternative to online file storage or an FTP client.
